before going to production.

Steps:
1. Log in to https://developer.apple.com
2. Go to Certificates, Identifiers & Profiles > Merchant IDs
3. Select your merchant ID > Click "Download" next to Domain Verification
4. Replace the contents of this file with the downloaded file (no extension, no changes)
5. Verify at: https://walkoutofficial.com/.well-known/apple-developer-merchantid-domain-association

The file must be served as plain text at this exact path with no auth required.
Vercel serves files in public/ statically — no additional config needed.
